Class ContainerSSEPolicyMismatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable

            • oracle.cloudstorage.ftm.exception.ContainerSSEPolicyMismatch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ContainerSSEPolicyMismatch
extends ClientException
    Object's container and segments container have different server-side encryption (SSE) policies. This exception is thrown by upload APIs when the static large object's container and its segment's container have different SSE policies.
